\begin_layout Standard
Credit rating is an 
\series bold
evaluation
\series default
 of the credit worthiness, ordered by the potential debtor from an independent
 ratin agency.
 It is applicable for corporations, governments and even individuals.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The information released by these agencies typically include 
\series bold
credit rating
\series default
 (short-term / long-term assessment), 
\series bold
rating watch
\series default
 (short-term update) and 
\series bold
rating outlook
\series default
 (long-term update)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
